data.body:
multiple urls in maven

repositories {
  maven { url "http://......." }
  maven { url "https://......" }
}

How do I know that the Timer is running?

I can see is_active() but this is not changing when I use start() or stop() see #4175.


Can we add something like this? Otherwise it is always true.

```
void Timer::start() {
	time_left=wait_time;
	active = true;
	_set_process(true);
}

void Timer::stop() {
	time_left=-1;
	active=false;
	_set_process(false);
	autostart=false;
}
```
